Users with DDL rights on database objects At Instance Level SELECT * FROM `mysql`.`user` WHERE (`mysql`.`user`.`user` not like 'mysql.%') AND ( `user`.`Create_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Drop_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Grant_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`References_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Index_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Alter_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Super_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Execute_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Create_view_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Create_routine_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Alter_routine_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Create_user_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Event_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Trigger_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Create_role_priv` = 'Y' OR `user`.`Drop_role_priv` = 'Y') ;
At DB/Schema Level - Users with DDL rights on database objects Ensure only administrative users are returned in the result set. SELECT * FROM mysql.db where (`db`.`Grant_priv` = 'Y' OR `db`.`References_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Index_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Alter_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Create_tmp_table_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Lock_tables_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Create_view_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Show_view_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Create_routine_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Alter_routine_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Execute_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Event_priv`= 'Y' OR `db`.`Trigger_priv`) and user not like 'mysql.%';
